ων\u003C/placeName>\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Ἡράκλειον\u003C/name> \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname type=\"patronym\">Νύμφωνος\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> \u003Cname>\u003Cw part=\"I\">Π\u003Cunclear>ε\u003C/unclear>\u003C/w>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>ἀρετᾶς ἕνεκα\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text of I.Segesta\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>To Zeus. The people of the Segestans (have dedicated this statue of) Herakleios Pe[---] son of Nymphon, on account of his excellence\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" source=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\">\n                \u003Cp>A Zeus. Il popolo dei Segestani (ha onorator/ha eretto la statua di) Herakleios, figlio di Nymphon, Pe[---], per il suo valore [transl. from I.Segesta]\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                   \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ampolo and Erdas\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2019\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>G3\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\">https://biblio.inscriptio